07:06.583 --> 07:08.709
I Shin-Don't.

07:09.709 --> 07:11.500
Well, when I see something wrong,

07:11.583 --> 07:13.750
it's my job to do something about it!

07:14.709 --> 07:16.500
Why don't you do something
about your breath?

07:16.583 --> 07:18.417
You could use a mint, sister!

07:19.625 --> 07:20.875
Uh...

07:26.041 --> 07:28.291
Respectful. Very, very respectful.

07:28.375 --> 07:29.917
Dojo's full of respect.

07:32.959 --> 07:34.291
Thank you, Jerry.

07:34.375 --> 07:36.417
I've learned everything I need to know.

07:45.000 --> 07:48.208
Look who just got a shipment
