08:39.291 --> 08:43.959
I made the decision about making you
a grandmaster at Otai, and it's--

08:44.041 --> 08:45.792
Yes! Yes! I knew it!

08:45.875 --> 08:48.792
So long, suckers! Grandmaster out!

