09:00.625 --> 09:03.041
If you cannot trust your students,

09:03.542 --> 09:05.208
I cannot trust you.

09:05.291 --> 09:07.709
What? I'm not gonna...

09:08.417 --> 09:11.291
But I told people
and I moved out of mother...

09:11.834 --> 09:13.125
