with your students

12:10.125 --> 12:13.083
and they finally told me
the truth about you.

12:13.166 --> 12:14.667
Oh, great.

12:14.792 --> 12:16.750
So now you know
that I chew on my toenails,

12:16.834 --> 12:18.333
