what kind of man you are,

12:38.417 --> 12:41.291
and we'd be honored to have you at Otai.

12:51.083 --> 12:53.208
Yes, get in here.

12:53.291 --> 12:54.917
You guys stink.

12:55.500 --> 12:57.542
<i>♪ And no matter how much
I chop and punch ♪</i>

12:57.625 --> 13:00.417
<i>♪ It's not as cool
As kickin' it with you ♪</i>

13:01.125 --> 13:04.917
