18:08.792 --> 18:10.542
We have no white belts.

18:10.625 --> 18:13.291
You will be grandmaster to students

18:13.375 --> 18:15.458
who are already champions.

18:16.041 --> 18:18.000
I'll go see if the car is here.

18:39.625 --> 18:41.917
Hey, I wonder who
the new head sensei will be.

18:42.000 --> 18:44.625
Well, hopefully me. I interviewed for it.

18:44.709 --> 18:46.625
So if, uh, we go in there
and I'm waiting to meet us,

18:46.709 --> 18:49.083
- don't be surprised.
- Just go.

18:54.834 --> 18:56.458
Rudy, what are you doing here?

18:57.750 --> 18:59.709
I decided to stay.

18:59.792 --> 19:00.834
Why?

19:00.917 --> 19:03.375
Well, because you guys showed me
that here...

19:04.208 --> 19:05.667
I can make a difference.

19:07.000 --> 19:08.625
Look, you can have
all the money in the world,

19:08.709 --> 19:10.542
but if you don't have
what we have right here,

19:10.625 --> 19:11.625
you got nothing.

19:13.208 --> 19:14.208
To friends.

19:15.500 --> 19:18.333
Jerry, volunteering can be very rewarding.

19:18.875 --> 19:20.750
What was it that you were supposed to do?

19:20.834 --> 19:23.583
I was supposed to bring meals
and help out some old man.

19:23.667 --> 19:25.834
Well, not only are you gonna do it,

19:25.917 --> 19:27.291
but I'm gonna go with you!

19:27.417 --> 19:29.166
And no matter where life takes us,

19:29.250 --> 19:31.667
we'll always be connected
by the Wasabi code.

19:33.709 --> 19:35.125
One final Wasabi?

19:39.917 --> 19:41.291
Wasabi!

19:42.959 --> 19:44.375
Nice. Again.

19:45.792 --> 19:46.750
That was good.

19:46.834 --> 19:47.834
All this...

19:47.917 --> 19:49.625
Just so we can go on a date.

19:49.709 --> 19:52.083
You know what? You're worth it.

19:53.250 --> 19:54.792
Kick!

19:54.875 --> 19:56.166
Kick!

19:56.625 --> 19:59.041
Jerry, why'd you do this for me?

19:59.125 --> 20:00.917
What I did was wrong, bro.

20:01.333 --> 20:03.333
I shouldn't have taken credit
for something you did.

20:03.417 --> 20:04.375
Thanks, Jerry.

20:07.000 --> 20:08.417
Congratulations, Jerry.

20:09.041 --> 20:10.500
You're now a black belt.

20:12.166 --> 20:15.750
- Thank you, sensei.
- Look at you, man. I'm so proud.

20:16.291 --> 20:18.542
They say you never forget your first love.

20:20.375 --> 20:22.000
And I know I never will.

20:23.625 --> 20:25.291
Remember what Rudy said,

20:26.166 --> 20:29.417
no matter where we go,
we'll always be connected.

20:30.500 --> 20:33.208
I can't believe
how far you guys have come.

20:33.750 --> 20:36.709
- Look at you! Come on!
- Oh, yeah!

20:41.125 --> 20:43.166
We're really glad
you decided to stay, man.

20:43.750 --> 20:46.250
We know you're gonna be able to help
a lot of other kids.

20:47.291 --> 20:49.291
They tried to make you
fly coach, didn't they?

20:49.375 --> 20:51.542
It's none of your business, Kim!

20:53.792 --> 20:55.125
Welcome home, sensei.

20:58.417 --> 20:59.667
All right, now line up.

21:03.875 --> 21:05.542
- Hup!
- Hup! Hup!

21:05.625 --> 21:06.959
Wasabi!

21:08.959 --> 21:10.834
- All four cameras.
-

21:10.917 --> 21:13.041
I would make the perfect General Douglas!

21:17.500 --> 21:19.125
Uh... Oh, no...

21:19.208 --> 21:20.208
What's the line?

21:21.291 --> 21:23.375
And that's all the letters
of the alphabet.

21:23.458 --> 21:25.500
Well, that's still too many.

21:25.834 --> 21:27.375
- A traitor.
-

21:29.000 --> 21:30.291
You need to hit the gym, bro.

21:57.041 --> 21:58.000
<i>Poor soul.</i>

22:02.000 --> 22:02.959
<i>Yes!</i>
